 Inventory Management System (Java Console App)

A simple, interactive console-based inventory management system built using Java. The application allows users to:

-  Add new products
-  View all products
- ️ Update product price or quantity
-  Remove products
-  View inventory in sorted order (by product name)

 Project Structure

InventoryManagementSystem/
│
├── src/
│   ├── Main.java
│   ├── Model/
│   │   └── Product.java
│   ├── UI/
│   │   └── UserInterface.java
│   └── Utilities/
│       └── InventorySystem.java
│
├── README.md
└── .gitignore


Concepts Used
    Object-Oriented Programming
    Java Collections (TreeMap)
    Exception Handling
    Modular Design

    